name: chromatophores
description: 5. years ago, scientists researched the biological method chameleons use to camouflage themselves attempting to apply it to tech. though successful, they mistakenly used intelligence gathering robots as their first guinea pigs. these circuits developed a mind of their own, and now slither around earth spying on humans. cover your webcam all you want, but the ones recording might already be in front of your eyes. collect to attract solitude. inscribed by tenorless circa 2019 // genesis collection
